sub_title: Head of Bid & Design, International at Haworth
summary:
Experienced professional with a true global mindset; having worked in various industries and positions around the world. 

Currently residing in Amsterdam, working internatonally and cross-culturally with our team of Tender Managers & Designers located in our offices in Hungary, Portugal, India, Malaysia and Singapore to support our Global Accounts and local sales teams in both AP & EMEA, ensuring consistently high standards of support throughout the region.
